name: Diplomats of the Celestial Theft
description: After losing many family members to decay and frailty within the Moribund Mists, those of the Diplomats of the Celestial Theft who made it out are strong. And certainly stronger than they look. They're also known for their skill at retrieving long lost relicsâ€¦ via methods savory and unsavory. Now armed with knowledge of the stars, moons, and tides, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
